title: Spliced Business Formations within 8 Quarters for Texas (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFSBF8QTOTALNSATX (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFSBF8QTOTALNSATX) for an alternative.

This series combines (splices) https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF8QNSATX and https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF8QNSATX to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within 8 quarters.
